title: Aquatop Replacement Coarse Blue Filter Pad – Fits Forza FZ13 UV Canister Filters, Aquarium Filter Refills, Keeps Water Crystal Clear, Fish Filter Cartridge for Dirt & Debris
features: REPLACEMENT CARBON INSERTS: This aquarium filter media is a replacement for filter pads in your Aquatop FORZA Series canister filter.
KEEP CRYSTAL CLEAR WATER: These tank filters are great for your filtration system and will help keep your aquarium water crystal-clear.
FITS AQUARIUM UV CANISTER FILTERS: These fish tank filter pads are pre-cut to fit Aquatop’s aquarium filter FZ13 UV for both fresh and saltwater tanks.
MADE OF STRONG MATERIAL: The FORZA cartridge layer mechanically removes organic particles, foreign debris, and excess foot for easy removal from your fish tanks and turtle tanks.

EASY TO USE & INSTALL: These replacement pads are extremely easy to use and install. Replace the Filter Insert filled every 4-6 weeks. Aquariums with heavier livestock loads may require more frequent replacement.
description: AquaTop's FZ13 UV Replacement Coarse Filter Pads mechanically remove organic particles, foreign debris, and excess food. They are suitable for freshwater and saltwater and are pre-cut to fit the Aquatop FZ13 UV Canister Filters.
